uni.hamburg.yamms.math.fft
Class Spec

java.lang.Object
  uni.hamburg.yamms.math.fft.Spec

public class Spec
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the Fourier transform specification for objects derived from the FFT class. This interface is inspired by the "guru interface" from the FFTW3 library (www.fftw.org).

Author:
Gunnar Selke
